）美国0830【海军因新冠病毒的疑虑要求第六舰队自我隔离】两名未具名美国海军官员透露，第六舰队下令各舰艇在访问欧洲港口之间要进行为期14天的自我隔离。
Two unidentified U.S. Navy officials said the Sixth Fleet ordered a 14-day self-imposed quarantine between ships visiting European ports.
该命令将使第六舰队与美国太平洋舰队的先前命令保持一致。
The order will align the Sixth Fleet with previous orders of the United States Pacific Fleet.
0800【累计确诊病例达122例，死亡9例】据CNN消息，美国疾控中心3日晚通报称，累计确诊新冠肺炎病例达122例，死亡9例。
A cumulative total of 122 cases and 9 deaths have been confirmed, the CDC said on Wednesday night.
这一数据包括核算检测推定阳性的患者，即在地方实验室检测呈阳性，但还需要疾控中心进一步确认。
This data includes accounting for presumed positive patients, that is, tested positive in a local laboratory, but further confirmation by the CDC is required.
确诊病例中有48名是从国外撤回的美国公民0800【美联储宣布降息50个基点】美国联邦储备委员会3日宣布将联邦基金利率目标区间下调50个基点到1%至1.25%的水平，这是美联储今年以来首次降息。
The Federal Reserve cut the federal funds rate target range by 50 basis points to between 1 percent and 1.25 percent, the first time the Federal Reserve has cut interest rates this year.
0800【谷歌取消年度会议Google I/O，欧洲员工居家办公】谷歌宣布取消预定于5月12至24日举行的2020年度 Google I/O会议。
Google cancels annual Google I / O, European Employee Home Office Google announced it would cancel its 2020 Google I / O conference, scheduled to take place from May 12 to 24.
已经购票的人可以获得全额退款，如购买2021年度会议的票无需再次登记。
Those who have already purchased tickets will receive a full refund, such as the purchase of tickets for the 2021 Conference without re-registration.
意大利0800【新增428例确诊病例，累计确诊2502例】当地时间3月3日18时，意大利民防部门负责人、新冠病毒应急委员会专员安杰洛·博雷利通报称，意大利共累计确诊2502例新型冠状病毒感染肺炎病例。
Italy 0800 [428 new confirmed cases, a cumulative total of 2,502 confirmed cases] March 3, 2008 At 18: 00 local time, Italian Civil Defence Commissioner Angelo Borelli informed me that a total of 2,502 new cases of coronavirus-infected pneumonia had been diagnosed in Italy.
其中，现存病例2263例，较前一天增加428例；死亡病例累计79例，较前一天增加27例；累计160例治愈，较前一天增加11例。
Of these, 2263 cases remained, 428 more than the previous day, 79 deaths were recorded, 27 more than the previous day, and 160 cases were cured, an increase of 11 cases over the previous day.
已对超过25800人进行了新冠病毒检测筛查。
More than 25,800 people have been screened for the new crown virus.
世卫组织0800【世卫组织：新冠肺炎有着独一无二的特性】总干事谭德塞在例行新闻发布会上表示，新冠肺炎病毒有着独一无二的特性，尽管它和流感有着相似之处，以同样的方式传播，但从现在掌握的数据来看，还是有很多的不同。
WHO 0800 [WHO: New Crown Pneumonia Has A Unique Character] Director-General Lindsay Tupper said at a regular news conference that the virus had unique characteristics and, although it had similarities with the flu and spread in the same way, there were many differences from the data available.
“新冠肺炎的传播效率不如流感，传播似乎并非由未出现症状的人所主导。
"Coronary pneumonia is not as effective as influenza, and transmission does not seem to be dominated by people without symptoms.
同时它会引起比流感更为严重的疾病。
And it can cause more serious illnesses than flu.
现在尚无任何疫苗或治疗剂，但它可以被控制。
There is no vaccine or therapeutic agent, but it can be controlled.
”谭德塞说。
'she said.
0800【全球共发现90893份确诊病例，3110例死亡】谭德塞通报称，截至3月3日中午新冠肺炎疫情以来全球共发现90893份确诊病例，3110例死亡。
0800 [90893 confirmed cases and 3,110 deaths worldwide] As of midday on March 3, 90893 confirmed cases and 3,110 deaths had been detected worldwide, Tan said.
在过去的24小时内，中国新增确认病例数位129例，这也是自1月20日以来最少的一天。
In the past 24 hours, 129 new cases have been confirmed in China, the lowest number since January 20.
中国之外新增病例1848例，80%来自于韩国、伊朗和意大利三个国家。
Out of 1,848 new cases outside China, 80% came from South Korea, Iran and Italy.
0800【呼吁增加医疗防护用品供给】谭德塞表示，全球范围内医疗防护用品短缺正在限制许多国家应对新冠肺炎疫情的能力。
[Calls for more medical supplies] A global shortage of medical supplies is limiting the ability of many countries to cope with the outbreak of pneumonia in the New Crown, says Tanner.
他呼吁各国政府和相关企业紧急行动起来，使医疗防护用品的全球供应量在现有基础上增加40%。
He called on Governments and relevant businesses to act urgently to increase the global supply of medical protection supplies by 40 per cent from the current level.
世卫组织估计，为应对新冠肺炎疫情，全球每月需要8900万个医用口罩、7600万副医用检查手套和160万副护目镜。
WHO estimates that 89 million medical masks, 76 million medical examination gloves and 1.6 million goggles are needed each month to respond to the outbreak.
西班牙0800【西班牙确诊病例达165例，有死亡患者被误诊】马德里疫情最为严重，上升至56例。
Spain 0800 [Spain confirmed 165 cases, the death of patients were misdiagnosed "Madrid the most serious epidemic, to 56 cases.
此外，瓦伦西亚大区出现西班牙第1例患者因新冠肺炎死亡，其死亡时间是2月13日。
In addition, the first case of death from pneumonia in Spain occurred in Valencia, on February 13.
这表明，西班牙第二波疫情早已开始。
This suggests that a second wave of Spanish epidemics has already begun.
同时暴露这个患者被误诊，一直被当地医院当成一般肺炎处理。
It was also revealed that the patient had been misdiagnosed and had been treated as pneumonia by the local hospital.
英国0800【政府公布应对新冠肺炎行动计划】政府将考虑关闭学校，鼓励公民在家工作，并减少大规模集会，以减缓新冠肺炎的传播。
The government will consider closing schools, encouraging citizens to work from home and reducing mass gatherings to slow the spread of pneumonia in the New Crown.
英国累计确诊新冠肺炎病例51例。
Cumulatively, 51 cases of new crown pneumonia were diagnosed in UK.
挪威0800【两名乘客检测呈阴性，挪威解除对德国邮轮的隔离】这艘名为“爱达奥拉”号的邮轮上有两名德国乘客，他们在一周前曾与一名已知的新冠病毒感染者有过接触。
NORWAY 0800 [two passengers tested negative] Norway has unsealed its German cruise ship, the Idaola, with two German passengers on board who a week ago had been in contact with a person known to be infected with the virus.
挪威方面对这两名乘客进行了检测，并于当天晚间宣布了检测结果：并未感染新冠病毒。
Norway tested the passengers and announced late that day that they were not infected with the new cap virus.
列支敦士登0800【确诊首例新冠肺炎病例】列支敦士登一名近期去过瑞士的公民被确诊感染新冠肺炎。
Liechtenstein 0800 [first confirmed case of Newly Coronary Pneumonia] A citizen of Liechtenstein who has recently been to Switzerland has been diagnosed with pneumonia.
阿根廷0800【确诊首例新冠肺炎病例】患者有意大利旅行史。
Argentine 0800 The patient has a history of traveling in Italy.
智利0800【确诊首例新冠肺炎病例】患者是一名33岁的医生，过去一个月内曾前往包括新加坡在内的多个东南亚国家。
Chile 0800 The patient, a 33-year-old doctor, has traveled to several Southeast Asian countries, including Singapore, in the past month.
伊朗0800【紧急服务部负责人感染新冠病毒，23名议员感染】伊朗卫生部3日披露的最新数据显示，伊朗已有累计2336例病例，其中77例死亡。
Iran has 2336 cases of human swine flu, including 77 deaths, according to the latest figures released Wednesday by Iran's Health Ministry.
议会中已经有23名议员感染新冠病毒。
Twenty-three members of Parliament have been infected with the new crown virus.
此外，紧急服务部负责人感染新冠病毒。
In addition, the head of Emergency Services contracted the New Crown Virus.
0800【伊朗暂时释放54200名监狱囚犯】CNN援引半官方通讯社ISNA消息，伊朗3日宣布，暂时释放54200名监狱囚犯，以防止新冠病毒疫情在监狱内传播。
0800 [Iran Temporarily Releases 54200 Prison Inmates] CNN quoted ISNA, the parastatal news agency, as saying on Wednesday that 54,200 prison inmates would be provisionally released to prevent the spread of the new crown virus in prison.
日本0820【累计确诊新冠肺炎患者超1000例】日本厚生劳动省4日表示，日本的新冠肺炎感染者（包括“钻石公主”号邮轮在内）已超过1000人。
Japan has more than 1,000 people newly infected with pneumonia, including Princess Diamond, the ministry said Thursday.
0800【新确诊19人，累计确诊999例】截至日本当地时间3月3日23时，日本累计确诊新冠肺炎病例999例，因新冠肺炎死亡累计12人。
0800 [19 new cases confirmed, a cumulative total of 999 confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia, 12 cumulative deaths due to new crown pneumonia in Japan as of 2300 local time on March 3, 2007.
0800【国际奥委会：2020东京奥运会将如期举办】国际奥委会主席巴赫表示，国际奥委会继续全力支持2020东京奥运会，并鼓励所有运动员充满信心全力以赴，继续为2020东京奥运会做准备。
IOC President Bach said the IOC continues to give its full support to the 2020 Tokyo Olympics and encourages all athletes to do their utmost and with full confidence to continue preparations for the 2020 Games.
国际奥委会新闻发言人表示，基于现有证据，没有理由更改2020东京奥运会，将按原计划于2020年7月24日至8月9日期间举行。
A spokesman for the IOC said there was no reason to change the 2020 Games on the basis of available evidence and that it would be held between July 24 and August 9, 2020 as originally planned.
韩国0800【确诊病例突破5000】截至下午4点，韩国境内感染新冠肺炎确诊病例增至5186例，较当天零时新增374例。
South Korea confirmed cases of pneumonia rose to 5,186 by 4 p.m., 374 more than at 00pm on the same day.
世界银行0800【向受影响的国家提供120亿美元支持】世界银行集团将通过快速通道实施一揽子计划，帮助发展中国家加强卫生系统，包括更好地获得卫生服务，以保护人们免受这一流行病的影响，加强疾病监测，加强公共卫生干预，并与私营部门合作，减少对经济的影响。
World Bank 0800 [$12 Billion Support to Affected Countries] The World Bank Group will fast-track a package to help developing countries strengthen health systems, including better access to health services to protect people from the epidemic, strengthen disease surveillance, strengthen public health interventions, and work with the private sector to reduce economic impacts.
该一揽子融资计划将在全球范围内进行协调，支持基于国家的应对措施，资金来自国际开发协会、国际复兴开发银行和国际金融公司。
The package will be coordinated globally in support of country-based responses, with funding from the International Development Association, the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development and the International Finance Corporation.
